  "tasbihatScreenSubtitle": "OTUTO EKPERE",
  "tasbihatScreenDescription": "Nduzi zuru ezu nke otuto a na-agụ n’oge na mgbe ekpere kwa ụbọchị gasịrị — na-eso omenala Ahl al-Bayt (a).",
  "tasbihatArba3Title": "TASBIḤĀT AL-ARBAʿA",
  "tasbihatArba3Subtitle": "A na-agụ ya na rakʿah nke 3 na nke 4",
  "tasbihatArba3Info": "N’iwu Shia, Tasbiḥāt al-Arbaʿa na-anọchi Surah al-Fatiha na rakʿah nke 3 na nke 4 nke Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib, na Isha. Ọ bụ iwu (wājib) ịgụ ya otu ugboro, ma a na-akwado (mustaḥabb) ịgụ ya ugboro atọ.",
  "tasbihatArba3Translation": "Otuto dịrị Allah · Otuto niile bụ nke Allah\nEnweghị chi ọzọ ma e wezụga Allah · Allah bụ Onye Kasị Ukwuu",
  "tasbihatArba3CompleteTitle": "Agụchaala",
  "tasbihatArba3CompleteMessage": "Ka a nabata ekpere gị — Āmīn",
  "tasbihatArba3TapHint": "Pịa mgbe agụchara ugboro ọ bụla",
  "tasbihatZahraSubtitle": "Mgbe ekpere ọ bụla gasịrị · mkpụrụ 100",
  "tasbihatZahraOriginLabel": "Mmalite",
  "tasbihatZahraHadith": "Lady Fatima al-Zahra (sa) rịọrọ Onyeamụma ﷺ ka ọ nye ya ohu. Ọ sịrị: \"Ka m gosi gị ihe ka mma? Gụọ Subḥānallāh ugboro 33, Alḥamdulillāh ugboro 33, na Allāhu Akbar ugboro 34 mgbe ekpere ọ bụla gasịrị. Nke ahụ ka mma karịa ohu nye gị.\"",
  "tasbihatZahraHadithSource": "— Bihar al-Anwār, Vol. 85",
  "tasbihatZahraOpenCounter": "Meghee Ngụkọ Tasbīḥ",
  "tasbihatDuasTitle": "DUA A NA-AKWADO",
  "tasbihatDuasSubtitle": "Mgbe i mezuchara ekpere gị",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiTitle": "Āyat al-Kursī",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiWhen": "Mgbe ekpere iwu ọ bụla gasịrị",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiSource": "Surah al-Baqarah 2:255",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiNote": "Onye ọ bụla na-agụ Āyat al-Kursī mgbe ekpere iwu ọ bụla gasịrị, ọ dịghị ihe guzo n’etiti ya na paradaịs ma e wezụga ọnwụ. Imam al-Bāqir (a) kwuru na ọ bụ otu n’ime amaokwu kacha ukwu na Qur’an.",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatTitle": "Ṣalawāt",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatWhen": "Mgbe ekpere ọ bụla gasịrị · na-emechi arịrịọ niile",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatSource": "Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) — Al-Kāfī",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatNote": "Izipu ngozi n’elu Onyeamụma ﷺ na ezinụlọ ya dị ọcha (Āl Muḥammad) ka a na-akwado iji mechie dua ọ bụla. Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) kwuru: \"Dua ọ bụla na-adọpụ uche ruo mgbe ị zitere ṣalawāt n’elu Muḥammad na ezinụlọ ya.\"",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajTitle": "Duʿā al-Faraj",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajWhen": "Mgbe ekpere ọ bụla gasịrị · maka Imam nke oge anyị",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajSource": "Imam al-Ḥasan al-ʿAskarī (a) kụziri ya",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajNote": "Dua fun ìfarahàn Imam al-Mahdī (af), Imam kẹtàlá, tí baba rẹ kọ́. A máa ń ka a nígbà púpọ̀ lára àwọn Musulumi Shia lẹ́yìn àdúrà gẹ́gẹ́ bí ìṣe ìbáṣepọ̀ pẹ̀lú Imam tó wà láàyè.",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaTitle": "Tasbīḥ nke Lady Fāṭima",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaWhen": "Mgbe Maghrib na Isha gasịrị · a na-akwado ya nke ukwuu",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaSource": "Imam al-Bāqir (a) — Biḥār al-Anwār",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaNote": "Imam al-Bāqir (a) kwuru na ịgụ Tasbīḥ al-Zahrā mgbe Isha gasịrị tupu ụra ka mma karịa rakʿah 1000 nke ekpere onwe onye. Ìhè ya na-arịgo eluigwe.",
